{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247950/extras/logo_2.png?t=1730623274\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247950/extras/0.png?t=1730623274\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247950/extras/boss.gif?t=1730623274\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fast-paced arena shooter action</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Six unlockable player characters with unique abilities and starting gear</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Five distinctly themed levels with increasing difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 120 weapons and items to unclock and try out</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Five intense multi-stage boss-fights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 50 distinct enemies with unique attack patterns and stats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247950/extras/1.png?t=1730623274\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247950/extras/utils_showcase_gif.gif?t=1730623274\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every world-saving hero needs his gadgets. After all, one doesn't come to a shootout empty-handed!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Weapons - Shoot, hit, and slash! From pistols and rocket launchers to more exotic specimens, weapons are the foundation and crucial element of gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Active Items - Think carefully about whether it's the right moment to use an active item, as it may take some time to recharge!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Passive Items - From mystical artifacts to... old junk. Passive items will largely define how each run unfolds. Some increase statistics, or allow summoning allied creatures, but others... may have quite unusual and more complex effects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Utility Items - Medkits, grenades, ammo boxes, and many more. These items are for onetime use, but they can prove helpful in various situations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247950/extras/2.png?t=1730623274\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247950/extras/char_select_gif.gif?t=1730623274\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each of the unlockable characters possesses a unique active skill and set of statistics meaning that choice of character directly influences the dynamics of the gameplay. Each character embodies a different archetype, ensuring that every player, regardless of their preferred playstyle, will find something right for them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247950/extras/2024-10-2901-21-42online-video-cutter.com-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1730623274\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">More info coming soon</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247950/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730623274","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247950/page.bg.jpg?t=1730623274","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247950/062e782ba598f390d6afbe447e8817aebb87e6ae/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730623274","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/324795